data.text:
Forms Library

Print these forms and send the completed forms to DFAS following the instructions provided.

Please note: If you click on a form and you see a message that says "Please wait..." you will need to download the form to your computer or device before you can open and use it. Right click on the link to the form, select "Save link as..." and a popup box will appear to allow you to save the form. Once you open the form, you will need to click on "Enable All Features" in order to view and fill in the form.
